{"id": 1141, "title": "Ticket #1141: default session duration is 3600 in 7.5.0", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe param table contains an entry for SEC_DEFAULT_SESSION_DURATION.  It is set to 3600.  This has two probably unintended effects:\n\n<p></p><ol>\n<li>daemons such as startds advertising to a collector will only get a 1h session instead of a 1 day session, which was the previous default.\n\n<p></p></li><li>tools such as condor_status get a 1h session instead of a 60s session.\n</li></ol>\n\n<p>I am removing this entry from the param table, because the param table is not currently appropriate for params that are looked up with SecMan::getSecSetting().</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Jan-26 12:51</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/7d7ce6d0019ef89ef25285542c1823132401bffe\">[16971]</a></span>: Fixed unintended 3600s default session duration. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1141\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1141'); return false;\" title=\"default session duration is 3600 in 7.5.0\">#1141</a></span>  (By Dan Bradley )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Jan-26 12:51</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/b0f100466160ee190c00e6af3a01b533e38ac641\">[25236]</a></span>: Documented fixes for SEC_&lt;access-level&gt;_SESSION_DURATION. <span class=\"ticket\"><a cla